_sText:
Hey!

This is my first released Destruction(De_) Map.
It's called de_colors because in the Map are all native Colors.
I tried to optimized the Map as much as possible.
It have High FPS(100-200) and it has a good Gameplay.
I recommened to play this Map with up to 32 Players, but it has 64 Spawns.

-VERY balanced
-good gameplay/teamplay
-Colorful
-good Tactic Gameplay
-High Fps(100-200)

GIVE IT A TRY! :D
